br />\n本人亦唔想再見到有人因為呢個港共政權而含冤入獄"},{"pid":"29a44f849874902dabf478991cc00bb203419fe7","tid":1267111,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6ogywo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6ogywo.png&h=a84d61c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f426ef3320d23c301d2dfe45cf7aba0b7ab094b9","tid":1267111,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9661444f5d1a7d76622ac2e8a3445313ecf63d1","tid":1267111,"uid":205449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:57:23.000Z","msg":"文宣組麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54a8a0611c756dd1f4032b53c26901bf7775fa88","tid":1267111,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e8c81bf5f3c526e9d39255b74b0eac58bf2067e","tid":1267111,"uid":37869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:55:37.000Z","msg":"尋求政治庇護<br />\n為件事增添更多不確定性<br />\n好過喺預見的計劃中慢慢死去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n我覺得如果德國或者其他國家批准香港難民申請<br />\n會係一個好大既誘因<br />\n逼美國同歐盟通過唔同既人權法案<br />\n起碼比起依家咁樣<br />\n越來越丟淡件事<br />\n最後不了了之好"},{"pid":"445d4e5ea15832f9623572223630b7fcd0d15125","tid":1267111,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:59:02.000Z","msg":"同埋反送中係全球咁多國家都反對既嘢<br />\n相信比起幾年前王台仰佢地更加容易獲得難民資格"},{"pid":"5433801877b7b828cc77270c1134367efafafb3a","tid":1267111,"uid":241006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:01:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afd4a726e5d051c7bc2874b7f88c5e3d8ddbf64d","tid":1267111,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:07:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b74f60a6b479fb123ffa20f6e2a649b21c0cb65","tid":1267111,"uid":259381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score